{"tid":30492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連巴及一眾管理員有冇諗過唔再派邀請碼?","createTime":"2016-12-09T08:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T10:05:19.000Z","uid":30745,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d11e6beef746a58af55fe4d4400bf371bdba6367","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"Lihkg成立或多或少同HKGplus事件有關，連巴派邀情碼接濟巴打們係一件好事，當初我都認為肯買hkgplus嘅都應該係高登會員，所以覺得冇咩事<br />\n<br />\n但係宜家睇下，5p林立，你都有班波台狗假膠都算啦，有班人真係吾系甘牙咁足成頁都自我感覺良好，認為自己冇錯，仲有一班殘體字狗，admin你地可唔可以諗下辦法阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最簡單一係唔好再派，一係取消哂所有邀請碼會員啦，我自己都係邀請碼會員，但如果為左個科林好，我情願冇左個ac佢<br />\n<br />\n隔離m版整到成個dicuss咁，最慘係呢邊個風氣好似上去discuss咁，坦白講句咁落去只要早逝佢改番apss版，啲巴打只會番番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301508f978a7b9d9a9c5e686e2616fbd61e1cb18","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194a175857dde2b78941134a3bca2eacf473d662","tid":30492,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d33564a2fa01243f121a0307fad5a15b3e03d4f","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔招多啲人連巴食屎呀?😨<br />\n<br />\n依家最緊要係做旺個場，愈多人愈好呀ching</blockquote><br />\n量重要得嚟質得好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfef4e3a018e62bafc2ea544e180b575a339b45","tid":30492,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3dbbb01f13c828b68684aad0a2316bf87b539b2f","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>push</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf9ff0888ac4d97e40e76a61c7feee74e390