login<br />\n咁個APi可以verify account password<br />\n之後就開到account得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n不過又係會攪到成班sms會員返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d760296ad54d1748525d90db95ad14d716775e9","tid":30492,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你整invite code<br />\n咪即係叫人買會員<br />\n咪又係有5毛出現<br />\n<br />\n一係有冇得整個API<br />\n經個API用高登account login<br />\n咁個APi可以verify account password<br />\n之後就開到account得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n不過又係會攪到成班sms會員返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n字<br />\n未就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢招至少確保到佢地係會員<br />\n都有限度確保佢地知道以前高登點行<br />\n唔會講吾系甘珍<br />\n唔會打殘體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<br />\n連去競爭對手到verify?<br />\n早洩整幾千個假AC直頭可以反攻"},{"pid":"0905835a1918a77e2ff04e5a1d273477bb7a7124","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你整invite code<br />\n咪即係叫人買會員<br />\n咪又係有5毛出現<br />\n<br />\n一係有冇得整個API<br />\n經個API用高登account login<br />\n咁個APi可以verify account password<br />\n之後就開到account得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n不過又係會攪到成班sms會員返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n字<br />\n未就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢招至少確保到佢地係會員<br />\n都有限度確保佢地知道以前高登點行<br />\n唔會講吾系甘珍<br />\n唔會打殘體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<br />\n連去競爭對手到verify?<br />\n早洩整幾千個假AC直頭可以反攻</blockquote><br />\n呢樣野可以用其他野證明嘅，應該(我唔識呢1方面野啦下)<br />\n不過至少我想講嘅係再邀請碼注冊一定要連埋身前作為高登會員嘅證明"},{"pid":"f6b33d6999788715e5bac9a724b145d098809d65","tid":30492,"uid":30214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"唔派邀請碼我d fd開唔到acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e7f68f984c9ce3073435dbaabd9139df884155","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔派邀請碼我d fd開唔到acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係本身高登都係用isp阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8786f0c8e3aaf9e52d0a171f7ec221e00476d612","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"推到管理員肯入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918ab1aff9baed7942b67c9e78d06326253df145","tid":30492,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔派邀請碼我d fd開唔到acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係本身高登都係用isp阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日多幾百個 連巴就賺幾千<br />\n比我都會繼續派<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0f4fcf8e318a124e19276a77e61a93398bb84a","tid":30492,"uid":50069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n字<br />\n未就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢招至少確保到佢地係會員<br />\n都有限度確保佢地知道以前高登點行<br />\n唔會講吾系甘珍<br />\n唔會打殘體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<br />\n連去競爭對手到verify?<br />\n早洩整幾千個假AC直頭可以反攻</blockquote><br />\n呢樣野可以用其他野證明嘅，應該(我唔識呢1方面野啦下)<br />\n不過至少我想講嘅係再邀請碼注冊一定要連埋身前作為高登會員嘅證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家只不過係講緊有一大堆人「講緊」自己有高登account 但係冇左API email<br />\n你要處理呢堆人開lihkg會員<br />\n除左自己整個api我真係諗唔到可以點做<br />\nLogin完之後up圖？<br />\n先唔好講人手對<br />\n睇改圖都睇死你啦"},{"pid":"7dedbec8a145cbd02e2bbd8245a9f487da50c390","tid":30492,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔派邀請碼我d fd開唔到acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係本身高登都係用isp阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日多幾百個 連巴就賺幾千<br />\n比我都會繼續派<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新買個啲好似註冊唔到lihkg"},{"pid":"6479a0356bd9635cb904856a5ad9f4ecdcf1606d","tid":30492,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:30:38.000Z","msg":"ban鳩哂邀請碼會員啦 , isp都冇就做cd rom la屌"},{"pid":"41ebcd75ad4040f94a560fb9b13b421d5fb927c8","tid":30492,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"5p 唔係收錢做事 如果唔想咁多5p 應該屌柒佢地 我相信佢地會收儉"},{"pid":"4da24d45773c4517957eab9ff6438784be346530","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n字<br />\n未就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢招至少確保到佢地係會員<br />\n都有限度確保佢地知道以前高登點行<br />\n唔會講吾系甘珍<br />\n唔會打殘體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<br />\n連去競爭對手到verify?<br />\n早洩整幾千個假AC直頭可以反攻</blockquote><br />\n呢樣野可以用其他野證明嘅，應該(我唔識呢1方面野啦下)<br />\n不過至少我想講嘅係再邀請碼注冊一定要連埋身前作為高登會員嘅證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家只不過係講緊有一大堆人「講緊」自己有高登account 但係冇左API email<br />\n你要處理呢堆人開lihkg會員<br />\n除左自己整個api我真係諗唔到可以點做<br />\nLogin完之後up圖？<br />\n先唔好講人手對<br />\n睇改圖都睇死你啦</blockquote><br />\n拿唔好怪我左膠口吻<br />\n呢點真係要大家討論有咩可行方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef9800d84892b4a0e9cd13157f4b18b14748b4a","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔派邀請碼我d fd開唔到acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係本身高登都係用isp阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日多幾百個 連巴就賺幾千<br />\n比我都會繼續派<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新買個啲好似註冊唔到lihkg</blockquote><br />\n冇新唔等於舊唔係5p狗"},{"pid":"75f53bac7968cb95c2150825ade932b9f63562f4","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5p 唔係收錢做事 如果唔想咁多5p 應該屌柒佢地 我相信佢地會收儉</blockquote><br />\n問題係高登仔係度慢慢變成小眾<br />\n情況如同香港人同中國蝗蟲咁"},{"pid":"098f073f74021816a35bd61e4b3f50cf898870b6","tid":30492,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ban鳩哂邀請碼會員啦 , isp都冇就做cd rom la屌</blockquote><br />\n最極端嘅做法<br />\n真係忍無可忍果時就應該咁做"}]}